entifier to be included in the resulting income report (eg. your customer identifier or SSN).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"externalReference"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Explicitly choose the version of the Income Check engine.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"engineVersion"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If provided, the Tink Link session will be initialized with a session to securely configure and pre-fill data in Tink Link."}]}],"name":"sessionID"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The unique name of the provider (eg. "},{"code":"sbab-bankid","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"). If this is provided, the provider will be chosen for the user. If not, the user can choose the provider in a list. If the given parameter is not a valid provider, the user will see an error screen."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"inputProvider"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"groupDisplayName"},{"type":"text","text":" of a bank group (eg. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sparkassen"},{"type":"text","text":"). If provided, the user is taken directly to the branch selection for that group. If the group has no branches, behaves like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"inputProvider"},{"type":"text","text":". If invalid, falls back to standard bank selection."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"inputGroup"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pre-fills the username field for supported providers. Providing this makes most sense if the username is a general username, valid for multiple banks (like a SSN)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"inputUsername"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The block to execute when the Income Check product flow finished or if an error occurred."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"